{"tid":1353420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[元朗恐襲]網傳受襲人仕可claim 港鐵第三者責任保險","createTime":"2019-07-23T03:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:44:58.000Z","uid":12558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21864dfd13900d9668333ddaf05ace2387a20fa9","tid":1353420,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"麻煩share出去, 元朗事件傷左既去 claim返 港鐵第三者保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗站白衣黨無差別襲擊途人事件︰<br />\n本人今日曾致電港鐵公司，代表港鐵公司既 馮偉程先生( 當天當值經理) 表示, 就元朗站白衣黨無差別襲擊途人事件，可以正式向地鐵公司遞交書面通知，申請第三者保險賠償港鐵，港鐵公司聲稱收到遞交後, 會有專員處理 (並不代表一定會賠償)<br />\n如有疑問，請致電港鐵熱線︰2881 8888 馮偉程先生 內線電話: 1206 ，如遇馮偉程先生休假或病假，請致電另一當值服務經理 陳先生, 內線電話︰1208<br />\n<br />\n以書面或Fax或網站上的意見提交方式遞交，內容包括︰<br />\n<br />\n1. 當時狀況<br />\n2. 要求賠償<br />\n3. 聯絡方法<br />\n<br />\n郵寄地址︰九龍灣偉業街33號德福廣場港鐵總部大樓 港鐵公司 公司事務處收<br />\n<br />\n網上提交: <a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Fcontact_us.html&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUigy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=0e71f18c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html</a><br />\n(謹記，一定要選擇 請回覆 電話 / 電郵)<br />\n<br />\nFax: 2208 3161<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dswxgcs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdswxgcs.png&h=da554368&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b91e7d8ec852163dd6abce2852d7c36a53160ce3","tid":1353420,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:15:52.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9e569bf9cb9d60ea1e6d7e3821cf5b37365489c7","tid":1353420,"uid":90015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"a8530a80bf8458f880971ff3eb1205b967853bc1","tid":1353420,"uid":90015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位!<br />\n如果道歉有用，點解仲要法律! <